these are the steps i followed to install SASS:
1. Installed Node Version Manager (NVM) using:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash
2. Restarted the terminal and installed Node.js version 20.16 using:
   nvm install 20.16
3. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 using:
   npm install sass -v 3.7.4